(40, 15, 15, 41, 7, 17, 17, 'Declare unto us this parable', 'Disciples'' Inquiry About Parables', 'Both passages emphasize the disciples'' desire for clarification on Jesus'' parables. Peter''s question in Matthew and the disciples'' inquiry in Mark reflect a shared theme of seeking understanding.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 15, 15, 43, 16, 29, 29, 'Declare unto us this parable', 'Disciples'' Understanding of Teachings', 'This connection highlights the disciples'' desire for clarity in Jesus'' teachings. In both passages, the disciples express a need for straightforward explanations, indicating their struggle to grasp his messages.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
